DWM-5.9 - http://dwm.suckless.org/
==================================
update.sh  - Update DWM sources. Before this - updating DWM by `pacman -S dwm`.
patche.sh  - Apply patches from patches dir.
install.sh - Install DWM in ArchLinux.


PATCHES - http://dwm.suckless.org/patches/
==========================================
dwm-5.8.2-pertag.diff     - This patch keeps layout, mwfact, barpos and nmaster (if installed) per tag.
dwm-5.9-movestack.diff    - This plugin allows you to move clients around in the stack and swap them with the master.
dwm-5.9-pwkl.diff         - Basically, this patch implements per-window keyboard layout support in dwm.
dwm-5.9-statuscolors.diff - This patch enables colored text in the status bar.
dwm-5.9-viewontag.diff    - follow a window to the tag it is being moved to.


CREATE PATCH
============

cd modified-dwm-directory/..
diff -up original-dwm-directory modified-dwm-directory > dwm-X.Y-yourpatchname.diff
